<<Chapter 1. Hello ET_HER>>

4839 * 3508 pixel PNG 3/25/2022

This is the first artwork of the <ET_HER's PRISM> series.

The main theme of this collection is<Metaverse system> and my lovely OC, ET_HER, will introduce you to my <Metaverse>

What is the future of <Metaverse> that we are looking forward to? Or how will it be made?

<Metaverse, Web 3.0, DAO, and tokens/NFT>

We've learn these words by NFT community on Twitter/Discord or whatever each of us joined to.

And this syndrome created a new type of globalization, similar but slightly different from past's one.

Let's jump into the new globalization!
